# SchemaLift — environment variable template
# Copy to .env.local for local overrides (never commit .env.local)
#
# No required vars for MVP — all config is stored in the SQLite DB
# and Windows Credential Manager via the app UI.
#
# Uncomment the block below to pre-seed a test PostgreSQL connection
# during development (optional):
#
# TEST_PG_HOST=localhost
# TEST_PG_PORT=5432
# TEST_PG_DATABASE=mydb
# TEST_PG_USER=postgres
# TEST_PG_PASSWORD=secret
